Package jp.co.rakuten.util.collection

Containers with I/F of like 'C++ STL'.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
StdContainer<T> Basic interface of container.
StdIterator<T> Iterator like C++ STL.
StdMap<K,V> Associative container like std::map of C++ STL.
StdMultiMap<K,V> Associative container like std::multimap of C++ STL.
StdMultiSet<T> Associative container like std::multiset of C++ STL.
StdRandom<T,K> Random accessable base interface of container.
StdRandomMulti<T,K> Random accessable interface of overlapping key is allowed.
StdRandomStartWith<T,K> Random accessable interface of range search.
StdRandomUnique<T,K> Random accessable interface of overlapping key is not allowed.
StdSequence<T> Sequence accessable interface of container.
StdSet<T> Associative container like std::set of C++ STL.
 

Class Summary
CompatibleIterable<T> Convert I/F to java.lang.Iterable.
CompatibleIterator<T> Convert I/F from range of StdIterator to java.lang.Iterator.
CompatibleReverseIterable<T> Convert I/F with reverse to java.lang.Iterable.
CompatibleReverseIterator<T> Convert I/F with reverse from range of StdIterator to java.lang.Iterator.
ConstStdIterator<T> Unmodifiable iterator ( wrapped StdIterator ).
Pair<FIRST,SECOND> The pair container.
 

Package jp.co.rakuten.util.collection Description

Containers with I/F of like 'C++ STL'. And wrappers to Java native iterator.
